      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ALL FOR IRISH (1) turned in a plain effort last time when seventh at this track over 320m behind No More Trouble (18.89) in a Mix 2/3. Can atone. APPIN WAY (2) jumped from a middle draw last time and could manage only fourth and beaten 2.25 lengths (19.62) at Bulli. Comes through a solid form race last start. Should be thereabouts. SHOT OF FAITH (8) doesn't win out of turn. Finished in the minors latest when third (18.78) at this track and may be close to breaking through. Has a good record here at this journey. Hard to beat again. EXTREMELY POTENT (6) is worth consideration.",
